data.description: Welcome to your new home in the heart of Edgewater. This beautiful 3-bed/ 2-bath home boasts a large, comfortable living space and is nestled on a generous lot measuring 80x125 ft.As you step inside, you'll appreciate the inviting ambiance of this well-maintained residence. The thoughtfully designed kitchen features stainless steal appliances, lots of cabinetry,  new refrigerator, and a large pantry. The primary bedroom has an ensuite bathroom, so you'll enjoy all the comfort and privacy you need. The additional bedrooms are perfect for family, guests, or even a home office. Step outside to view the jewel of this property - the huge backyard! This space provides lots of room for activities in both the front and back patios with a fenced in backyard. Easy access to local amenities, shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Whether you're looking to explore nearby parks, hit the beach, or enjoy water activities, this prime location offers it all.
